Language Comprehension unique skill
only the protagonist possesses via Appraisal.

Core Mechanics:

Effect: The protagonist instantly and perfectly understands, reads, writes, and speaks any language he encounters — human, monster, ancient, demonic, elven, beastkin, magical runes, or even completely alien scripts.
This includes spoken words, written text, signs, and magical incantations.
On books/items: Automatically translates the entire content into Japanese in the protagonist’s mind or overlays translated text only he can see.

Key Rules:
It is passive and always active — no MP cost, no activation needed.
Provides perfect nuance, idioms, tone, and cultural context (he understands jokes, sarcasm, poetry, and hidden meanings).
Does not grant the ability to teach the language to others.
The rest of the world still has real language barriers. Only the protagonist bypasses them completely.

Strategic Flavor:
This skill gives the protagonist a massive information and social advantage. He can read forbidden ancient tomes, understand secret monster languages, eavesdrop on any conversation, and negotiate with any race without translators. No one else realizes he is doing this.
